### 4.4 Background Strategy — Video Background (Hero Only)

Video background **hanya** dipakai di **Welcome Screen + Hero Section** agar tidak membebani performa. Sisanya menggunakan background solid.

| Aspek               | Detail                                                                                                |
| ------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Posisi**          | Welcome screen & Hero section saja (full-viewport)                                                    |
| **Konten Video**    | Loop pendek (10-15 detik): soft bokeh lights, floating gold particles, atau kain sutra bergerak pelan |
| **Overlay**         | Gradient overlay semi-transparan (`rgba(0,0,0,0.4)` → transparent) agar teks tetap terbaca            |
| **Fallback**        | Foto prewedding sebagai `poster` jika video gagal load                                                |
| **Performance**     | `<video muted autoplay loop playsinline>`, resolusi max 720p, format WebM + MP4                       |
| **Mobile**          | Auto-switch ke foto statis (video terlalu berat di mobile)                                            |
| **Section lainnya** | Background solid: `--off-white` (#FAF9F6) dan `--cream` (#F5F0E8) bergantian                          |

### 4.5 Animation Engine — GSAP + Lenis

Kombinasi **GSAP** + **Lenis** (keduanya gratis) untuk animasi dan smooth scrolling:

| Library           | Fungsi                                                                     |
| ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **GSAP Core**     | Animasi dasar: fade, scale, translate, stagger                             |
| **ScrollTrigger** | Memicu animasi berdasarkan scroll position (section reveal, parallax, pin) |
| **Lenis**         | Smooth scrolling seluruh halaman — feel premium, open-source               |

**Setup:**

```typescript
// lib/gsap.ts — GSAP + ScrollTrigger registration
import gsap from "gsap";
import { ScrollTrigger } from "gsap/ScrollTrigger";

gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);
export { gsap, ScrollTrigger };
```

```typescript
// lib/lenis.ts — Lenis smooth scroll + GSAP integration
import Lenis from "lenis";
import { ScrollTrigger } from "gsap/ScrollTrigger";

export function initSmoothScroll() {
  const lenis = new Lenis({
    duration: 1.2,
    easing: (t) => Math.min(1, 1.001 - Math.pow(2, -10 * t)),
    smoothWheel: true,
  });

  // Sync Lenis dengan GSAP ScrollTrigger
  lenis.on("scroll", ScrollTrigger.update);

  function raf(time: number) {
    lenis.raf(time);
    requestAnimationFrame(raf);
  }
  requestAnimationFrame(raf);

  return lenis;
}
```

