## 9. Verification Plan

### 9.1 Automated / Browser Testing

| Test               | Method  | Command / Steps                                                              |
| ------------------ | ------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Build succeeds     | CLI     | `npm run build` — harus 0 error                                              |
| Dev server runs    | CLI     | `npm run dev` — bisa diakses di `localhost:3000`                             |
| Guest page renders | Browser | Navigate ke `localhost:3000/to/test-guest` → verifikasi semua section tampil |
| RSVP submit        | Browser | Isi form RSVP → submit → cek data masuk di Supabase                          |
| Guestbook submit   | Browser | Tulis ucapan → submit → cek status "pending" di DB                           |
| Admin login        | Browser | Navigate ke `/admin/login` → login → redirect ke dashboard                   |
| CSV import         | Browser | Upload CSV di `/admin/guests` → cek guest baru terbuat di DB                 |
| QR check-in        | Browser | Hit `/api/guests/checkin` with valid token → verify `checked_in = true`      |

### 9.2 Manual Verification (User)

1. **Visual & Animation Review** — User membuka undangan di mobile dan desktop, memverifikasi estetika sesuai expectation (slow-zoom, fade-in audio, scroll animations)
2. **Responsive Layout** — Test di berbagai ukuran layar (375px, 768px, 1440px)
